                    "reply_user_id": "17025146",
                    "content": "你现在还不知道我这个的nb性，它现在可以指哪儿打哪儿，整个解释器就是一个goto的工具。\n比如while我现在这样推导：\nwhile c1{b1} else {b2}\n-&gt; while True{if c1{b1} else {b2,break}}\n-&gt; if c1{b1 goto if} else b2\n到这一层就能很简洁地实现了。看来我的设计已经捅破天了",
                    "likes": 0,
                    "unlikes": 0,
                    "replies": 0,
                    "top": 0,
                    "removed": 0,
                    "links": null,
                    "created_at": "2024-02-12 09:44:42",
                    "comment_from": "message",
                    "username": "小轩",
                    "user_avatar_path": "https://static1.xesimg.com/udc-o-user-avatar/20240907/TalzonWMSyKikgD5ZEDafJ9YyA_d75edba0b573c72c.png",
                    "reply_username": "吴宇航",
                    "emojis": [],
